snippet.textDisplay:
After Coke Studio Bangla season 1,  Season 2 is also producing just a series of masterpieces....

This is just marvelous... Hats off to everyone involved in this amazing composition and production...
The fusion of so many mesmerizing things with keeping the main folk thing intact is worthy of having really heart-felt respect to all of you. 
I like many lines in the lyric... specially when the song has so many things at a time, whereas you can't put so many things for the same few lines again and again. Only a few lines in a song just lose much expectation , as in the case of sonar dewra or like that; even in the case of Nodir kul, the few lines again and again has minimized the overall experience of the amazing composition of the masterpiece. 

But this song is delightfully done satisfying almost every types of expectation, specifically about the composition and the good amount of lyrics.       

Hats off again to the Total Team....and don't make things in  haste.... take considerable time and give such amazing masterpieces. Thank you from Bangladesh...
snippet.textOriginal:
